HFC Comments: Control Condition: MIXDMeasurement Section Codition: bWeather Condition: clerWind Velocity: 0Wind Direction: 0Unmeasured Flow Commen1mx.3msx.08depth Stage reset to 4.703 due to stage rising quickly during reset interval possibly due to evening wind picking up. Gauge is not close enough to water for quick DWL. Not enough time to perform second DWL. Old offset = 3.468 new = 3.655. MGH values taken from logger data with SRC of added.
